title: History Channel The Re Inventors Incinerating Toilet Xvid AC3
description: Proper disposal of sewage and waste is something all societies face if they are to prevent the spread of disease and epidemics. As populations have increased over the years so have the ideas for disposal, removal, and processing regarding waste. Join the Re-Inventors teams as they examine some of these and build some to see which are good ideas and which are crappy ones. MVGroup Forum avi
